{"tid":1088851,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"讀唔成書，做消防差佬係唯一選擇","createTime":"2019-04-02T10:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T12:41:26.000Z","uid":173617,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d62057612ea5569dda2ba0ffc9fe77cd11e5deb5","tid":1088851,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:51:25.000Z","msg":"中一至中六入爛仔學校，瘋狂溝學生妹，享受青春，唔撚洗温書，返part time賺生活費，做mk, 潮童。屋企人親戚覺得你無前途，係垃圾，但唔緊要，人地對你冇期望反而仲好。<br />\n預入唔到大學，但要夠分申請差佬最低學歷要求，中學成日去玩，接觸人多，有豐富社會經驗，半個古惑仔，符合差佬形象。人地温書就去操肌。<br />\n之後考差佬，月入24k。10年後起碼40k以上。未計可能升職。<br />\n4年後同屆同學先岩岩畢業，爭10皮學費，你已經賺左100幾萬。佢地揾野做起薪得13k，你已經有26-28k以上。轉埋消防，海關洗底，變左成功人仕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時班親戚轉晒肽，話要你做榜樣，自己個仔大學畢業先得13k。"},{"pid":"e7b724e2bca3d3d4cda0ff481ccd67576a0c7def","tid":1088851,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:52:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7efc61bf629f12826372657bf6bec0279ecfc46c","tid":1088851,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"短視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3251cabd24fef428229c106b5f7a734e344150","tid":1088851,"uid":199071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"日夜癲倒都不了，斷六親"},{"pid":"3a60b11d5afbc42ac2d992db72f6ac825663b362","tid":1088851,"uid":27247,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiMhod1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiMhod1.png&h=07b8d3d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2c63162eda5a2c26bcbd49d4aa9dbddbae77f5d","tid":1088851,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:14:21.000Z","msg":"消防唔易做架<br />\n你估玩下手握力當考試咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01f212f80199095b87dd656a9bfad5f9affad69","tid":1088851,"uid":239